{"id":575743,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/12/【cdtv】留恋牛年榴莲甜：错误治国理念的无限轮回/","date":"2017-12-30T07:50:35Z","modified":"2017-12-30T07:50:35Z","title":"【CDTV】留恋牛年榴莲甜：错误治国理念的无限轮回","content":"<p><video src=\"//f.us.sinaimg.cn/002tMoNOlx07gWidFQi401040200a73Z0k01.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=28&amp;Expires=1514621275&amp;ssig=f%2F661VZKPz&amp;KID=unistore,video\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"550\" height=\"315\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">﻿</span></video></p>\n<p>（<a href=\"https://weibo.com/tv/v/c38609cac2e971f7dda99d67256cc232?fid=1034:c38609cac2e971f7dda99d67256cc232\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">视频链接</a>）</p>\n<p><strong>附：部分视频对白</strong></p>\n<p>“先生，何以无为治国？”<br />\n“可以以贪治贪”<br />\n“贪官怎么能用？”<br />\n“理由其一：天下无官不贪？不怕官贪，就怕官有异志。故以反贪之名，提出异志贪官。这样既可以消除异己，又得到民众的拥戴。其二：贪官只要贪，你就有把柄在手。他若异志乃自找死路，故必与你同心同德。”<br />\n“如任用贪官而招惹民怨怎么办？”<br />\n“那就祭起反贪大旗，使天下皆知君王心系天下，尤恨贪官。”<br />\n“贪官民怨太大当如何处之？”<br />\n“杀之可也。抄其家，没其财。如是则民怨息，颂声起，又可收其财，何乐而不为？”<br />\n“所谓后发制人！”<br />\n“简而言之，用贪官以结其忠，弃贪官以肃异己，杀大贪以平民愤，没其财以充公用。”<br />\n宇文泰听后，深以为然！拜苏绰为尚书兼农卿。<br />\n然而历史的轨迹却并没有按照苏绰的预料发展，北周政权仅存20多年。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_575749\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/治国理念.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-575749\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/治国理念.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/治国理念.jpg 1384w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/治国理念-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/治国理念-768x433.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/治国理念-1024x577.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">视频截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13770],"tags":[13232,20561,22223,13026]}